Title: WowModelExplorer
Description: a WPF and Directx9, Directx11 implementation of model explorer of world of warcraft.  English and Chinese UI Interface, Mists of Pandaria 5.2Support.
HomeWiki:
Project Description
View Characters, Npcs, Items, Wmos of World of warcraft, including adding/removing character's equipments, playing animations and lots of other functions, full of a complete explorer application's features, Chinese and English language UI, Mists of Pandaria 5.2Support.

WPF 4.0 for UI and C# Intermediate library.

Latest update: http://sourceforge.net/projects/wowexplorer
